title: Onyx Webb: Book Five
description:
Lives continue to entwine. The web is getting more complicated and past and present collide.
 Onyx Webb is an epic weaving of lives across generations. The connections, twists, and turns, will surprise and delight you along the way. In this fifth book, Onyx is visited by Sister Katherine who has revenge on her mind. Koda is in a terrible accident that might be the end. Stan Lee is in the middle of a terrible crime. As always there are answers but even more questions in the pages of book five that will keep you hooked.
author: Richard Fenton
